<p>
    You can search by HEI name, SCHAC, Erasmus code, PIC.
    Please type a pattern and hit "Enter".
    Example search patterns:
</p>

<ul>
    <li>PL&lt;space&gt; - search for Polish HEIs (by Erasmus code)</li>
